---
---
<section class="section lifestyle-section">
  <div class="container lifestyle-grid">
    <div class="lifestyle-content">
      <h2>Engineered for Excellence</h2>
      <p>
        Our proprietary Ultra-Mist technology ensures an even, smooth application every time. Whether you're a professional artist or a DIY enthusiast, Spray Bazaar delivers the finish you deserve.
      </p>
      <ul class="lifestyle-list">
        <li><strong>No-Clog Valve:</strong> Guaranteed performance until the last drop.</li>
        <li><strong>High-Pressure Delivery:</strong> Consistent spray pattern in any orientation.</li>
        <li><strong>Quick-Swap Caps:</strong> Switch between detail and broad coverage in seconds.</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/tech" class="btn btn-outline">Explore the Tech</a>
    </div>
    <div class="lifestyle-images">
      <div class="image-large">
        <img src="/images/lifestyle.png" alt="Artist using spray" />
      </div>
      <div class="images-stacked">
        <img src="/images/lifestyle.png" alt="Spray detail" style="filter: grayscale(0.5) contrast(1.2);" />
        <img src="/images/lifestyle.png" alt="Color swatch" style="filter: brightness(0.7) sepia(0.3);" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .lifestyle-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .lifestyle-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }
  .lifestyle-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .lifestyle-list {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .lifestyle-list li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  .lifestyle-list li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  .btn-outline {
    border: 2px solid var(--text-dark);
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: var(--text-dark);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .lifestyle-images {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .image-large {
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 600px;
  }
  .image-large img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .images-stacked {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .images-stacked img {
    height: 290px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .lifestyle-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .lifestyle-images {
      order: -1;
    }
  }
</style>
